data.description:
Updated with huge new kitchen and open floor plan. Includes newer appliances. Very clean and move in ready. Updated windows, window air but very low electrical bills average only $44 per month! Master bedroom with door to large covered patio. Fenced yard and shed for shop or storage. Detached utility room with breezeway past carport to kitchen. Very nice! Only two blocks to Guadaulpe street and riverfront park.

Brokered And Advertised By: Texas Hill Country Properties
Listing Agent: Diane Dempsey
